{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","title":"MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol"}}}